Given that the questions of activity and involvement are central to the key claims in this case, the Court will allow the witness to answer accordingly. The Plaintiff will also have an opportunity of rebuttal to this matter.

@wetc You are asked to answer questions 1, 2, 3, 4, 4b, 6, 8, and 9 from the Defence.

Please advise the Court if you need any additional clarification before proceeding with your answers.
